ents/conversation/`): add a 'Pacing' card showing avg/min/max WPM and a one-line coaching tip based on the average (e.g., 'Try slowing down — fast pace can hurt clarity').\n\nThis is fluency-focused, complements (does not duplicate) shadowing/SSE/role-swap/quick-reply, is fully user-visible, and is testable: DAL unit tests for `get_pace_stats` + a router test asserting that posting `speaking_seconds` persists `pace_wpm` correctly.",
